<div class="tasty-recipes-quick-links">
	<a class="tasty-recipes-jump-link" href="#tasty-recipes-36954">Jump to Recipe</a><span>&middot;</span><a class="tasty-recipes-print-link" href="https://www.feastingathome.com/tomato-risotto/print/36954/">Print Recipe</a>
</div>

<p style="text-align: center;"><em>A summery Tomato Risotto highlighting juicy, sweet, vine-ripened tomatoes, and infused with <a class="tasty-link" rel="nofollow" target="_blank" data-tasty-links-append-disclosure href="https://bowlandpitcher.com/collections/spices-and-condiments/products/saffron-1">saffron</a>. &nbsp;Serve this as a vegetarian main, seasonal side dish, or top it off with smoky, &nbsp;pan-seared shrimp. Vegetarian-adaptable!</em></p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-36983" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%201200%201800'%3E%3C/svg%3E" alt="Summer Tomato Risotto with juicy vine-ripened tomatoes, and infused with saffron, can be served as a vegetarian main or sidedish, or topped off with smoky shrimp. #vegetarian #risotto #shrimprisotto " width="1200" height="1800" data-pin-title="Summery Tomato Risotto" data-pin-description="Summer Tomato Risotto with juicy vine-ripened tomatoes, and infused with saffron, can be served as a vegetarian main or sidedish, or topped off with smoky shrimp. #vegetarian #risotto #shrimprisotto " data-lazy-srcset="https://www.feastingathome.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tomato-Risotto_-23.jpg 780w, https://www.feastingathome.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tomato-Risotto_-23-200x300.jpg 200w, https://www.feastingathome.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tomato-Risotto_-23-683x1024.jpg 683w, https://www.feastingathome.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tomato-Risotto_-23-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://www.feastingathome.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tomato-Risotto_-23-1024x1536.jpg 1024w" data-lazy-sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" data-lazy-src="https://www.feastingathome.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tomato-Risotto_-23.jpg" /><noscript><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-36983" src="https://www.feastingathome.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tomato-Risotto_-23.jpg" alt="Summer Tomato Risotto with juicy vine-ripened tomatoes, and infused with saffron, can be served as a vegetarian main or sidedish, or topped off with smoky shrimp. #vegetarian #risotto #shrimprisotto " width="1200" height="1800" data-pin-title="Summery Tomato Risotto" data-pin-description="Summer Tomato Risotto with juicy vine-ripened tomatoes, and infused with saffron, can be served as a vegetarian main or sidedish, or topped off with smoky shrimp. #vegetarian #risotto #shrimprisotto " srcset="https://www.feastingathome.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tomato-Risotto_-23.jpg 780w, https://www.feastingathome.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tomato-Risotto_-23-200x300.jpg 200w, https://www.feastingathome.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tomato-Risotto_-23-683x1024.jpg 683w, https://www.feastingathome.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tomato-Risotto_-23-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://www.feastingathome.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tomato-Risotto_-23-1024x1536.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /></noscript></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><em>On a cool afternoon or any afternoon, take thee to the woods. There is a spirit there, ancient, waiting to soothe your soul. We call it time. ~D.M. Jenkins</em></p>
<p>Is there anything better than summer&#8217;s sweet and juicy tomatoes, picked right off the vine? I look forward to them every year, never tiring of their goodness.</p>
<p>Here they are blistered in a pan before going into a flavorful <a class="tasty-link" rel="nofollow" target="_blank" data-tasty-links-append-disclosure href="https://bowlandpitcher.com/collections/spices-and-condiments/products/saffron-1">saffron</a>-infused risotto. It&#8217;s hearty enough for a vegetarian main, or can be served a flavorful side dish to grilled fish and meats.</p>
<p>You can also top this off with Smoky pan-seared shrimp (or fish). &nbsp;An easy adaptable meal that can be kept vegetarian, or bumped up with a protein for meat-eaters.</p>
<h2 style="text-align: center;"><em>How to Make Tomato Risotto | 30-second video</em></h2>

<div class="adthrive-video-player in-post" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/VideoObject" data-video-id="1jn7bzGY" data-player-type="default" override-embed="default">
			<meta itemprop="uploadDate" content="2020-09-21T17:01:15.000Z" />
		<meta itemprop="name" content=" Tomato Risotto " />
		<meta itemprop="description" content="A simple recipe video for Tomato Risotto highlighting juicy, sweet, vine-ripened tomatoes, and infused with saffron. Serve this as a vegetarian main, seasonal side dish, or top it off with smoky, pan-seared shrimp. Vegetarian-adaptable!" />
		<meta itemprop="thumbnailUrl" content="https://content.jwplatform.com/thumbs/1jn7bzGY-720.jpg" />
		<meta itemprop="contentUrl" content="https://content.jwplatform.com/videos/1jn7bzGY.mp4" />
	</div>

<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-36958" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%201200%201800'%3E%3C/svg%3E" alt="This summery risotto is made with juicy vine-ripened tomatoes, and saffron and can be kept vegetarian or topped off with smoky shrimp. #vegetarian #risotto #shrimprisotto " width="1200" height="1800" data-pin-title="Tomato Risotto with Shrimp" data-pin-description="This summery risotto is made with juicy vine-ripened tomatoes, and saffron and can be kept vegetarian or topped off with smoky shrimp. #vegetarian #risotto #shrimprisotto " data-lazy-srcset="https://www.feastingathome.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tomato-Risotto.jpg 780w, https://www.feastingathome.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tomato-Risotto-200x300.jpg 200w, https://www.feastingathome.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tomato-Risotto-683x1024.jpg 683w, https://www.feastingathome.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tomato-Risotto-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://www.feastingathome.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tomato-Risotto-1024x1536.jpg 1024w" data-lazy-sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" data-lazy-src="https://www.feastingathome.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tomato-Risotto.jpg" /><noscript><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-36958" src="https://www.feastingathome.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tomato-Risotto.jpg" alt="This summery risotto is made with juicy vine-ripened tomatoes, and saffron and can be kept vegetarian or topped off with smoky shrimp. #vegetarian #risotto #shrimprisotto " width="1200" height="1800" data-pin-title="Tomato Risotto with Shrimp" data-pin-description="This summery risotto is made with juicy vine-ripened tomatoes, and saffron and can be kept vegetarian or topped off with smoky shrimp. #vegetarian #risotto #shrimprisotto " srcset="https://www.feastingathome.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tomato-Risotto.jpg 780w, https://www.feastingathome.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tomato-Risotto-200x300.jpg 200w, https://www.feastingathome.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tomato-Risotto-683x1024.jpg 683w, https://www.feastingathome.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tomato-Risotto-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://www.feastingathome.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tomato-Risotto-1024x1536.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /></noscript></p>
<h2><em>Ingredients in Tomato Risotto:</em></h2>
<ol>
<li>summer tomatoes!</li>
<li>onion</li>
<li>garlic</li>
<li><a class="tasty-link" rel="nofollow" target="_blank" data-tasty-links-append-disclosure href="https://amzn.to/30NeqsQ">veggie stock</a></li>
<li>short-grain rice</li>
<li><a class="tasty-link" rel="nofollow" target="_blank" data-tasty-links-append-disclosure href="https://bowlandpitcher.com/collections/spices-and-condiments/products/saffron-1">saffron</a></li>
<li><a class="tasty-link" rel="nofollow" target="_blank" data-tasty-links-append-disclosure href="https://amzn.to/3gphtxC">salt</a> &amp; pepper</li>
<li><a class="tasty-link" rel="nofollow" target="_blank" data-tasty-links-append-disclosure href="https://amzn.to/2RWPiLP">smoked paprika</a></li>
<li>a little pat of butter</li>
<li>parmesan</li>
</ol>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>The recipe starts with fresh, juicy summer tomatoes.</p>
<p><img data-pin-title="Summer Tomato Risotto with Saffron" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-36979" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%201200%20800'%3E%3C/svg%3E" alt="A summery Tomato Risotto made with juicy, sweet, vine-ripened tomatoes, and infused with saffron. &nbsp;Serve this as a vegetarian main, seasonal side dish, or top it off with smoky, &nbsp;pan-seared shrimp. Vegetarian-adaptable!" width="1200" height="800" data-pin-nopin="true" data-pin-description="A summery Tomato Risotto made with juicy, sweet, vine-ripened tomatoes, and infused with saffron. &nbsp;Serve this as a vegetarian main, seasonal side dish, or top it off with smoky, &nbsp;pan-seared shrimp. Vegetarian-adaptable!" data-lazy-srcset="https://www.feastingathome.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tomato-Risotto_.jpg 780w, https://www.feastingathome.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tomato-Risotto_-300x200.jpg 300w, https://www.feastingathome.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tomato-Risotto_-768x512.jpg 768w" data-lazy-sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" data-lazy-src="https://www.feastingathome.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tomato-Risotto_.jpg" /><noscript><img data-pin-title="Summer Tomato Risotto with Saffron" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-36979" src="https://www.feastingathome.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tomato-Risotto_.jpg" alt="A summery Tomato Risotto made with juicy, sweet, vine-ripened tomatoes, and infused with saffron. &nbsp;Serve this as a vegetarian main, seasonal side dish, or top it off with smoky, &nbsp;pan-seared shrimp. Vegetarian-adaptable!" width="1200" height="800" data-pin-nopin="true" data-pin-description="A summery Tomato Risotto made with juicy, sweet, vine-ripened tomatoes, and infused with saffron. &nbsp;Serve this as a vegetarian main, seasonal side dish, or top it off with smoky, &nbsp;pan-seared shrimp. Vegetarian-adaptable!" srcset="https://www.feastingathome.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tomato-Risotto_.jpg 780w, https://www.feastingathome.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tomato-Risotto_-300x200.jpg 300w, https://www.feastingathome.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tomato-Risotto_-768x512.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /></noscript></p>
<p>Use cherry or grape tomatoes, if possible. They are easiest to blister.</p>
<p><img data-pin-title="Summer Tomato Risotto with Saffron" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-36980" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%201200%20800'%3E%3C/svg%3E" alt="blistering tomatoes for risotto " width="1200" height="800" data-pin-nopin="true" data-pin-description="blistering tomatoes for risotto " data-lazy-srcset="https://www.feastingathome.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tomato-Risotto_-2.jpg 780w, https://www.feastingathome.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tomato-Risotto_-2-300x200.jpg 300w, https://www.feastingathome.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tomato-Risotto_-2-768x512.jpg 768w" data-lazy-sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" data-lazy-src="https://www.feastingathome.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tomato-Risotto_-2.jpg" /><noscript><img data-pin-title="Summer Tomato Risotto with Saffron" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-36980" src="https://www.feastingathome.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tomato-Risotto_-2.jpg" alt="blistering tomatoes for risotto " width="1200" height="800" data-pin-nopin="true" data-pin-description="blistering tomatoes for risotto " srcset="https://www.feastingathome.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tomato-Risotto_-2.jpg 780w, https://www.feastingathome.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tomato-Risotto_-2-300x200.jpg 300w, https://www.feastingathome.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tomato-Risotto_-2-768x512.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /></noscript></p>
<p>While they soften and blister in a skillet, start the risotto by sauteing the onion until golden and tender. Add the garlic.</p>
<p><img data-pin-title="Summer Tomato Risotto with Saffron" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-36978" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%201200%20800'%3E%3C/svg%3E" alt="how to make risotto- start with onions " width="1200" height="800" data-pin-nopin="true" data-pin-description="how to make risotto- start with onions " data-lazy-srcset="https://www.feastingathome.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tomato-Risotto_-4.jpg 780w, https://www.feastingathome.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tomato-Risotto_-4-300x200.jpg 300w, https://www.feastingathome.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tomato-Risotto_-4-768x512.jpg 768w" data-lazy-sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" data-lazy-src="https://www.feastingathome.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tomato-Risotto_-4.jpg" /><noscript><img data-pin-title="Summer Tomato Risotto with Saffron" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-36978" src="https://www.feastingathome.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tomato-Risotto_-4.jpg" alt="how to make risotto- start with onions " width="1200" height="800" data-pin-nopin="true" data-pin-description="how to make risotto- start with onions " srcset="https://www.feastingathome.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tomato-Risotto_-4.jpg 780w, https://www.feastingathome.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tomato-Risotto_-4-300x200.jpg 300w, https://www.feastingathome.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tomato-Risotto_-4-768x512.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /></noscript></p>
<p>Add the <a class="tasty-link" rel="nofollow" target="_blank" data-tasty-links-append-disclosure href="https://amzn.to/330HWOe">arborio rice</a> or short-grain rice.</p>
<p>Here I&#8217;m actually using a type of short-grain Spanish rice, typically used for Paella.</p>
<p><img data-pin-title="Summer Tomato Risotto with Saffron" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-36981" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%201200%20800'%3E%3C/svg%3E" alt="short grain Spanish rice-how to make risotto " width="1200" height="800" data-pin-description="short grain Spanish rice-how to make risotto " data-lazy-srcset="https://www.feastingathome.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tomato-Risotto_-3.jpg 780w, https://www.feastingathome.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tomato-Risotto_-3-300x200.jpg 300w, https://www.feastingathome.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tomato-Risotto_-3-768x512.jpg 768w" data-lazy-sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" data-lazy-src="https://www.feastingathome.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tomato-Risotto_-3.jpg" /><noscript><img data-pin-title="Summer Tomato Risotto with Saffron" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-36981" src="https://www.feastingathome.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tomato-Risotto_-3.jpg" alt="short grain Spanish rice-how to make risotto " width="1200" height="800" data-pin-description="short grain Spanish rice-how to make risotto " srcset="https://www.feastingathome.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tomato-Risotto_-3.jpg 780w, https://www.feastingathome.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tomato-Risotto_-3-300x200.jpg 300w, https://www.feastingathome.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tomato-Risotto_-3-768x512.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /></noscript></p>
<p>Saute the rice until it becomes translucent, 1-2 minutes.</p>
<p><img data-pin-title="Summer Tomato Risotto with Saffron" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-36976" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%201200%20800'%3E%3C/svg%3E" alt="how to make risotto " width="1200" height="800" data-pin-nopin="true" data-pin-description="how to make risotto " data-lazy-srcset="https://www.feastingathome.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tomato-Risotto_-6.jpg 780w, https://www.feastingathome.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tomato-Risotto_-6-300x200.jpg 300w, https://www.feastingathome.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tomato-Risotto_-6-768x512.jpg 768w" data-lazy-sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" data-lazy-src="https://www.feastingathome.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tomato-Risotto_-6.jpg" /><noscript><img data-pin-title="Summer Tomato Risotto with Saffron" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-36976" src="https://www.feastingathome.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tomato-Risotto_-6.jpg" alt="how to make risotto " width="1200" height="800" data-pin-nopin="true" data-pin-description="how to make risotto " srcset="https://www.feastingathome.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tomato-Risotto_-6.jpg 780w, https://www.feastingathome.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tomato-Risotto_-6-300x200.jpg 300w, https://www.feastingathome.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tomato-Risotto_-6-768x512.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /></noscript></p>
<p>Add enough warm broth or stock to cover the rice, about 2 cups, along with a pinch of <a class="tasty-link" rel="nofollow" target="_blank" data-tasty-links-append-disclosure href="https://bowlandpitcher.com/collections/spices-and-condiments/products/saffron-1">saffron</a>.</p>
<p><img data-pin-title="Summer Tomato Risotto with Saffron" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-36975" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%201200%20800'%3E%3C/svg%3E" alt="how to make risotto " width="1200" height="800" data-pin-nopin="true" data-pin-description="how to make risotto " data-lazy-srcset="https://www.feastingathome.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tomato-Risotto_-7.jpg 780w, https://www.feastingathome.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tomato-Risotto_-7-300x200.jpg 300w, https://www.feastingathome.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tomato-Risotto_-7-768x512.jpg 768w" data-lazy-sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" data-lazy-src="https://www.feastingathome.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tomato-Risotto_-7.jpg" /><noscript><img data-pin-title="Summer Tomato Risotto with Saffron" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-36975" src="https://www.feastingathome.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tomato-Risotto_-7.jpg" alt="how to make risotto " width="1200" height="800" data-pin-nopin="true" data-pin-description="how to make risotto " srcset="https://www.feastingathome.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tomato-Risotto_-7.jpg 780w, https://www.feastingathome.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tomato-Risotto_-7-300x200.jpg 300w, https://www.feastingathome.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tomato-Risotto_-7-768x512.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /></noscript></p>
<p>If your <a class="tasty-link" rel="nofollow" target="_blank" data-tasty-links-append-disclosure href="https://bowlandpitcher.com/collections/spices-and-condiments/products/saffron-1">saffron</a> is deep and red, it will only take a pinch. If it is lighter in color- like orange or yellow, it may take a couple of pinches. Crush it in your fingers before adding.</p>
<p><img data-pin-title="Summer Tomato Risotto with Saffron" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-36974" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%201200%20800'%3E%3C/svg%3E" alt="how to make risotto with saffron" width="1200" height="800" data-pin-nopin="true" data-pin-description="how to make risotto with saffron" data-lazy-srcset="https://www.feastingathome.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tomato-Risotto_-8.jpg 780w, https://www.feastingathome.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tomato-Risotto_-8-300x200.jpg 300w, https://www.feastingathome.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tomato-Risotto_-8-768x512.jpg 768w" data-lazy-sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" data-lazy-src="https://www.feastingathome.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tomato-Risotto_-8.jpg" /><noscript><img data-pin-title="Summer Tomato Risotto with Saffron" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-36974" src="https://www.feastingathome.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tomato-Risotto_-8.jpg" alt="how to make risotto with saffron" width="1200" height="800" data-pin-nopin="true" data-pin-description="how to make risotto with saffron" srcset="https://www.feastingathome.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tomato-Risotto_-8.jpg 780w, https://www.feastingathome.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tomato-Risotto_-8-300x200.jpg 300w, https://www.feastingathome.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tomato-Risotto_-8-768x512.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /></noscript></p>
<p>Then add the warm stock a cup at a time, stirring frequently, letting the rice absorb it, before adding any more.</p>
<p>Be patient here, this will take 20-25 minutes.</p>
<p>At the same time, chop up your cooled, blistered tomatoes and add these along with all their flavorful juices into to the risotto pot.</p>
<p><img data-pin-title="Summer Tomato Risotto with Saffron" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-36973" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%201200%20800'%3E%3C/svg%3E" alt="how to blister tomatoes " width="1200" height="800" data-pin-nopin="true" data-pin-description="how to blister tomatoes " data-lazy-srcset="https://www.feastingathome.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tomato-Risotto_-9.jpg 780w, https://www.feastingathome.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tomato-Risotto_-9-300x200.jpg 300w, https://www.feastingathome.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tomato-Risotto_-9-768x512.jpg 768w" data-lazy-sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" data-lazy-src="https://www.feastingathome.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tomato-Risotto_-9.jpg" /><noscript><img data-pin-title="Summer Tomato Risotto with Saffron" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-36973" src="https://www.feastingathome.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tomato-Risotto_-9.jpg" alt="how to blister tomatoes " width="1200" height="800" data-pin-nopin="true" data-pin-description="how to blister tomatoes " srcset="https://www.feastingathome.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tomato-Risotto_-9.jpg 780w, https://www.feastingathome.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tomato-Risotto_-9-300x200.jpg 300w, https://www.feastingathome.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tomato-Risotto_-9-768x512.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /></noscript></p>
<p>Keep adding stock a cup at a time, letting the rice absorb it, each time. &nbsp;I used about 6 3/4 cups of <a class="tasty-link" rel="nofollow" target="_blank" data-tasty-links-append-disclosure href="https://amzn.to/30NeqsQ">veggie stock</a> here, but depending on heat level and the type of rice, it may take more or less.</p>
<p><img data-pin-title="Summer Tomato Risotto with Saffron" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-36972" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%201200%20800'%3E%3C/svg%3E" alt="how to make tomato risotto " width="1200" height="800" data-pin-nopin="true" data-pin-description="how to make tomato risotto " data-lazy-srcset="https://www.feastingathome.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tomato-Risotto_-10.jpg 780w, https://www.feastingathome.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tomato-Risotto_-10-300x200.jpg 300w, https://www.feastingathome.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tomato-Risotto_-10-768x512.jpg 768w" data-lazy-sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" data-lazy-src="https://www.feastingathome.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tomato-Risotto_-10.jpg" /><noscript><img data-pin-title="Summer Tomato Risotto with Saffron" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-36972" src="https://www.feastingathome.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tomato-Risotto_-10.jpg" alt="how to make tomato risotto " width="1200" height="800" data-pin-nopin="true" data-pin-description="how to make tomato risotto " srcset="https://www.feastingathome.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tomato-Risotto_-10.jpg 780w, https://www.feastingathome.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tomato-Risotto_-10-300x200.jpg 300w, https://www.feastingathome.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tomato-Risotto_-10-768x512.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /></noscript></p>
<p>Once the rice becomes tender and creamy season with <a class="tasty-link" rel="nofollow" target="_blank" data-tasty-links-append-disclosure href="https://amzn.to/3gphtxC">salt</a>, pepper, <a class="tasty-link" rel="nofollow" target="_blank" data-tasty-links-append-disclosure href="https://amzn.to/2RWPiLP">smoked paprika</a>, a little butter and parmesan.</p>
<p><img data-pin-title="Summer Tomato Risotto with Saffron" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-36969" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%201200%20800'%3E%3C/svg%3E" alt="how to make vegetarian risotto " width="1200" height="800" data-pin-nopin="true" data-pin-description="how to make vegetarian risotto " data-lazy-srcset="https://www.feastingathome.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tomato-Risotto_-13.jpg 780w, https://www.feastingathome.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tomato-Risotto_-13-300x200.jpg 300w, https://www.feastingathome.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tomato-Risotto_-13-768x512.jpg 768w" data-lazy-sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" data-lazy-src="https://www.feastingathome.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tomato-Risotto_-13.jpg" /><noscript><img data-pin-title="Summer Tomato Risotto with Saffron" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-36969" src="https://www.feastingathome.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tomato-Risotto_-13.jpg" alt="how to make vegetarian risotto " width="1200" height="800" data-pin-nopin="true" data-pin-description="how to make vegetarian risotto " srcset="https://www.feastingathome.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tomato-Risotto_-13.jpg 780w, https://www.feastingathome.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tomato-Risotto_-13-300x200.jpg 300w, https://www.feastingathome.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tomato-Risotto_-13-768x512.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /></noscript></p>
<p>Some may prefer a &#8220;looser&#8221; risotto, one that lays flat in a bowl, so feel free to add more broth, right before serving to get the consistency exactly how you like it.</p>
<p>At the end, the secret to the flavor is getting the <a class="tasty-link" rel="nofollow" target="_blank" data-tasty-links-append-disclosure href="https://amzn.to/3gphtxC">salt</a> balance right.</p>
<p>If it is bland, add more <a class="tasty-link" rel="nofollow" target="_blank" data-tasty-links-append-disclosure href="https://amzn.to/3gphtxC">salt</a>, pepper and a pinch of chili flakes.</p>
<p>Finish with some lemon zest for a touch of brightness.</p>
<p><img data-pin-title="Summer Tomato Risotto with Saffron" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-36968" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%201200%20800'%3E%3C/svg%3E" alt="how to make vegetarian risotto with tomatoes and saffron " width="1200" height="800" data-pin-nopin="true" data-pin-description="how to make vegetarian risotto with tomatoes and saffron " data-lazy-srcset="https://www.feastingathome.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tomato-Risotto_-14.jpg 780w, https://www.feastingathome.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tomato-Risotto_-14-300x200.jpg 300w, https://www.feastingathome.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tomato-Risotto_-14-768x512.jpg 768w" data-lazy-sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" data-lazy-src="https://www.feastingathome.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tomato-Risotto_-14.jpg" /><noscript><img data-pin-title="Summer Tomato Risotto with Saffron" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-36968" src="https://www.feastingathome.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tomato-Risotto_-14.jpg" alt="how to make vegetarian risotto with tomatoes and saffron " width="1200" height="800" data-pin-nopin="true" data-pin-description="how to make vegetarian risotto with tomatoes and saffron " srcset="https://www.feastingathome.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tomato-Risotto_-14.jpg 780w, https://www.feastingathome.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tomato-Risotto_-14-300x200.jpg 300w, https://www.feastingathome.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tomato-Risotto_-14-768x512.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /></noscript></p>
<p>Serve this as a vegetarian main, or side dish. Or feel free to add shrimp.</p>
<p>If adding shrimp, season with the spice rub in the recipe card.</p>
<p><img data-pin-title="Summer Tomato Risotto with Saffron" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-36971" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%201200%20800'%3E%3C/svg%3E" alt="smoky shrimp rub " width="1200" height="800" data-pin-description="smoky shrimp rub " data-lazy-srcset="https://www.feastingathome.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tomato-Risotto_-11.jpg 780w, https://www.feastingathome.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tomato-Risotto_-11-300x200.jpg 300w, https://www.feastingathome.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tomato-Risotto_-11-768x512.jpg 768w" data-lazy-sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" data-lazy-src="https://www.feastingathome.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tomato-Risotto_-11.jpg" /><noscript><img data-pin-title="Summer Tomato Risotto with Saffron" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-36971" src="https://www.feastingathome.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tomato-Risotto_-11.jpg" alt="smoky shrimp rub " width="1200" height="800" data-pin-description="smoky shrimp rub " srcset="https://www.feastingathome.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tomato-Risotto_-11.jpg 780w, https://www.feastingathome.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tomato-Risotto_-11-300x200.jpg 300w, https://www.feastingathome.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tomato-Risotto_-11-768x512.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /></noscript></p>
<p>Pan-sear for a couple of minutes until golden and flavorful.</p>
<p><img data-pin-title="Summer Tomato Risotto with Saffron" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-36970" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%201200%20800'%3E%3C/svg%3E" alt="pan fried shirmp for risotto " width="1200" height="800" data-pin-description="pan fried shirmp for risotto " data-lazy-srcset="https://www.feastingathome.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tomato-Risotto_-12.jpg 780w, https://www.feastingathome.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tomato-Risotto_-12-300x200.jpg 300w, https://www.feastingathome.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tomato-Risotto_-12-768x512.jpg 768w" data-lazy-sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" data-lazy-src="https://www.feastingathome.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tomato-Risotto_-12.jpg" /><noscript><img data-pin-title="Summer Tomato Risotto with Saffron" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-36970" src="https://www.feastingathome.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tomato-Risotto_-12.jpg" alt="pan fried shirmp for risotto " width="1200" height="800" data-pin-description="pan fried shirmp for risotto " srcset="https://www.feastingathome.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tomato-Risotto_-12.jpg 780w, https://www.feastingathome.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tomato-Risotto_-12-300x200.jpg 300w, https://www.feastingathome.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tomato-Risotto_-12-768x512.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /></noscript></p>
<p>Top of the risotto with the flavorful shrimp.</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-36961" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%201200%201800'%3E%3C/svg%3E" alt="Summer Tomato Risotto with juicy vine-ripened tomatoes, and infused with saffron, can be served as a vegetarian main or sidedish, or topped off with smoky shrimp. #vegetarian #risotto #shrimprisotto " width="1200" height="1800" data-pin-title="Tomato Risotto with Shrimp " data-pin-description="Summer Tomato Risotto with juicy vine-ripened tomatoes, and infused with saffron, can be served as a vegetarian main or sidedish, or topped off with smoky shrimp. #vegetarian #risotto #shrimprisotto " data-lazy-srcset="https://www.feastingathome.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tomato-Risotto_-22.jpg 780w, https://www.feastingathome.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tomato-Risotto_-22-200x300.jpg 200w, https://www.feastingathome.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tomato-Risotto_-22-683x1024.jpg 683w, https://www.feastingathome.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tomato-Risotto_-22-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://www.feastingathome.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tomato-Risotto_-22-1024x1536.jpg 1024w" data-lazy-sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" data-lazy-src="https://www.feastingathome.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tomato-Risotto_-22.jpg" /><noscript><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-36961" src="https://www.feastingathome.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tomato-Risotto_-22.jpg" alt="Summer Tomato Risotto with juicy vine-ripened tomatoes, and infused with saffron, can be served as a vegetarian main or sidedish, or topped off with smoky shrimp. #vegetarian #risotto #shrimprisotto " width="1200" height="1800" data-pin-title="Tomato Risotto with Shrimp " data-pin-description="Summer Tomato Risotto with juicy vine-ripened tomatoes, and infused with saffron, can be served as a vegetarian main or sidedish, or topped off with smoky shrimp. #vegetarian #risotto #shrimprisotto " srcset="https://www.feastingathome.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tomato-Risotto_-22.jpg 780w, https://www.feastingathome.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tomato-Risotto_-22-200x300.jpg 200w, https://www.feastingathome.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tomato-Risotto_-22-683x1024.jpg 683w, https://www.feastingathome.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tomato-Risotto_-22-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://www.feastingathome.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tomato-Risotto_-22-1024x1536.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /></noscript></p>
<p>Obviously, if you have both meat-eaters and vegetarians in the same house, you can add shrimp to some and leave shrimp off others. Super easy. 😉</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter wp-image-36963 size-full" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%20780%201170'%3E%3C/svg%3E" alt="Summer Tomato Risotto with juicy vine-ripened tomatoes, and infused with saffron, can be served as a vegetarian main or sidedish, or topped off with smoky shrimp. #vegetarian #risotto #shrimprisotto " width="780" height="1170" data-pin-title="Tomato Risotto with Shrimp " data-pin-description="Summer Tomato Risotto with juicy vine-ripened tomatoes, and infused with saffron, can be served as a vegetarian main or sidedish, or topped off with smoky shrimp. #vegetarian #risotto #shrimprisotto " data-lazy-srcset="https://www.feastingathome.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tomato-Risotto_-19.jpg 780w, https://www.feastingathome.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tomato-Risotto_-19-200x300.jpg 200w, https://www.feastingathome.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tomato-Risotto_-19-683x1024.jpg 683w, https://www.feastingathome.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tomato-Risotto_-19-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://www.feastingathome.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tomato-Risotto_-19-1024x1536.jpg 1024w" data-lazy-sizes="(max-width: 780px) 100vw, 780px" data-lazy-src="https://www.feastingathome.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tomato-Risotto_-19.jpg" /><noscript><img class="aligncenter wp-image-36963 size-full" src="https://www.feastingathome.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tomato-Risotto_-19.jpg" alt="Summer Tomato Risotto with juicy vine-ripened tomatoes, and infused with saffron, can be served as a vegetarian main or sidedish, or topped off with smoky shrimp. #vegetarian #risotto #shrimprisotto " width="780" height="1170" data-pin-title="Tomato Risotto with Shrimp " data-pin-description="Summer Tomato Risotto with juicy vine-ripened tomatoes, and infused with saffron, can be served as a vegetarian main or sidedish, or topped off with smoky shrimp. #vegetarian #risotto #shrimprisotto " srcset="https://www.feastingathome.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tomato-Risotto_-19.jpg 780w, https://www.feastingathome.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tomato-Risotto_-19-200x300.jpg 200w, https://www.feastingathome.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tomato-Risotto_-19-683x1024.jpg 683w, https://www.feastingathome.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tomato-Risotto_-19-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://www.feastingathome.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Tomato-Risotto_-19-1024x1536.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 780px) 100vw, 780px" /></noscript><em class=""><strong>On the homefront:</strong></em>My husband started a nightly ritual of hot and cold dipping. Where we are staying in Santa Barbara there is a hot tub and a very cold pool. &nbsp;Yes, we&#8217;re spoiled. 😉 We wait until it&#8217;s dark outside, and the stars and moon are gloriously bright, and we start our practice, first in the hot, then in the cold and repeat over and over.</p>
<p class="">In the beginning, I couldn&#8217;t help how effortlessly Brian would slip into that freezing cold water, without a gasp, moonlight on his skin. I,&nbsp;on the other hand, would grit my teeth, gasp loudly and&nbsp;resist with all my might.&nbsp; When I asked him how he did that so painlessly, he simply said, &#8220;Embrace the cold&#8221;.</p>
<p class="">So several nights after that, I just started paying attention to what was happening as I stepped in that cold water. How my mind created fear around what was coming, how my body totally&nbsp;tensed in response to those thoughts.</p>
<p class="">My mind had made the cold out to be the enemy. It created a whole story around it. Eventually,&nbsp;I was able to see it for what it was. Just cold water. Something that would not kill me. 😉 &nbsp;I would be lying if I told you it&#8217;s easy now. But, surprisingly,&nbsp;it&#8217;s not quite as hard. It has been a&nbsp;good practice for me.</p>
<p class="">Of course, I can&#8217;t help but look at other areas of my life and how this applies. When I resist and listen to stories in my head, instead of just feeling the real experience,&nbsp;I stop the beautiful flow that so wants be, and in its place comes anxiety, restriction, suffering. &nbsp;When I let go of &#8220;stories&#8221;, embracing whatever is, life becomes easier and more effortless. I know this, but I forget.</p>
<p class="">I love how the physical world mirrors and&nbsp;reminds us of&nbsp;our inner work. To me, these everyday lessons are so digestible. &nbsp;So perfectly crafted for us. Kind of magic!</p>
