<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>Ok friends, I&#8217;m curious if you&#8217;ll like this one as much as we do. The leftover risotto gets even more flavorful after a couple of days (if it lasts that long!) as the flavors have a chance to meld. Just warm it back up in a pan on the stove with a little more broth or water.</p>
<p>Tell us what you think in the comments below with any adaptations you make.</p>
<p>Thanks and hope your week is well!</p>
<p>xoxo</p>
<p>Sylvia</p>
